Stay Young Forever?"

01:25:41.360 --> 01:25:44.840 align:middle line:84%
We were looking at diet
and exercise and lifestyle.

01:25:44.840 --> 01:25:47.930 align:middle line:84%
I met Dr. Valter Longo
to talk about his work.

01:25:47.930 --> 01:25:49.580 align:middle line:84%
And it was at the
time he was preparing

01:25:49.580 --> 01:25:52.070 align:middle line:84%
