01:26:02.300 --> 01:26:03.747 align:middle line:84%
And that was
repeated three times.

01:26:03.747 --> 01:26:06.080 align:middle line:84%
>> One of the things that our
large clinical trials have

01:26:06.080 --> 01:26:08.663 align:middle line:84%
shown is that at the very least
